  "text": "To show the effectiveness of our model on detections from different 2D pose detectors, we also experimented with the detections from CPM [CITATION_1] and from stacked-hourglass [CITATION_2] (SH) module which is not fine-tuned on Human3.6M dataset. We observe that even for the non-fine tuned stacked hourglass detections, our model achieves the state-of-the-art results. For detections from CPM, our model achieves competitive accuracy for the predictions.",
